	abstract = {A number of important philosophical problems are at the intersectionof logic and ontology. Both logic and ontology are diverse fieldswithin philosophy and, partly because of this, there is not one singlephilosophical problem about the relation between them. In this surveyarticle we will first discuss what different philosophical projectsare carried out under the headings of “logic” and“ontology” and then we will look at several areas wherelogic and ontology overlap.},
