@book{maurer_settlers_2013,
	edition = {1 edition},
	title = {Settlers of Catan Strategy Guide},
	abstract = {Are you hooked on Settlers of Catan but sick of losing to your friends?

Take your skills to the next level with some strategic thinking or face the continuing humiliation.

This Settlers of Catan Strategy Guide helps you understand the game on a deeper level. To become a more effective player you need to become a student of the game and almost treat it like an academic exercise.

The more you understand the game, the more you understand the subtleties and the more you understand human psychology the more likely you are to win. When you can read your opponents and stay several steps ahead in your mind your tactics will improve.

Settlers is not unlike chess in the need to have the ability to foresee all outcomes and how they will unfold. It involves many permutations based on what you do and what your opponents do. To make it more complicated you have several opponents to think about, not just one.

Reading strategy and putting it into practice will accelerate your growth as a player. Rather than just relying on trial and error and gathered experience you need to read widely and apply a little bit of scholarship to the game.

The key things to learn are:

Situational awareness and understanding the best options to take to win.
An understanding of your opponents strategies and how to combat them.
An aggressive winning mindset and the expectations of success.

Strategies of how to place your pieces and what resources to focus on are only part of the bigger picture. Reading your opponents mind, having a broad situational awareness and the ability to think many moves ahead are crucial traits to develop.

Like anything in life you improve by practicing and honing both your skills and your attitude. You have to work hard and practice. Improving takes time and dedication but we will help you get there.

Ultimately this Settlers of Catan Strategy Guide will mean you win more games and keep the bragging rights among your friends.},
